sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE ( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION LIKE "%game%" OR COURSEalias0.NAME LIKE "%game%" ) AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" ;
